+ *                   KEY ASSIGNMENT: PLAN A, LONG KEYS.
+ *
+ * DIRECTORY ITEMS
+ *
+ * |       60     | 4 | 7 |1|   56        |        64        |        64       |
+ * +--------------+---+---+-+-------------+------------------+-----------------+
+ * |    dirid     | 0 | F |H|  prefix-1   |    prefix-2      |  prefix-3/hash  |
