+/**
+ * save_file_hint - copy hint to reiser4 private struct file's part
+ * @file: file to save hint in
+ * @hint: hint to save
+ *
+ * This copies @hint to reiser4 private part of struct file. It can help
+ * speedup future accesses to the file.
+ */
